{
  "stem": "3360.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And the reason he did that-- at that point in time, they started to deport Jews who had come from Poland during this century.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And there were quite a few and had settled in Germany and made a good living there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "Their children were born there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "But they were from Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "I had several in my class in the Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "One was very wealthy, the other one was very smart.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And, you know, and we had a great time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And-- and they started to deport those Polish Jews to the Polish border.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "At which point, Poland did not want to accept them and quickly took away their Polish citizenship, which they-- which they still had.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And they became stateless.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "That was the worst of all evils, to be stateless.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And they were-- and they were hungry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "There was no-- there was nothing for them there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "They were like dumped into-- in-- they weren't concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "They were just dumped there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "They had nothing to eat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "They had no money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "They had nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "And so this young man, he was 17 years old, I guess had received a letter from his parents telling him in what desperate situation they are and to see if he could send them something.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "And what he had in mind, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "But he went to the embassy with a gun in his hand.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "Whether the gun went off by mistake-- he killed this minor German diplomat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "And that's what's set off the-- the happenings of Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
